{"tid":2431634,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［現實版關禮傑］紅磡天台屋遭縱火 南亞漢企晾衫架躍飛隔離樓逃生","createTime":"2021-03-03T20:12:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T11:41:18.000Z","uid":239336,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"42842a7c64cc50e7b7c3d8667922d6ae516840cc","tid":2431634,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T20:12:59.000Z","msg":"周三（3日）晚上約11時，紅磡華豐街7至9號一座唐樓，唐八樓天台後樓梯起火，並四處漫延，波及旁邊一間鐵皮屋，濃煙衝天，更一度傳出爆炸聲，約40名居民疏散至樓下暫避。消防到場後動用兩喉兩煙帽將火救熄，無人受傷。火警於35分鐘後救熄，調查後發現有4處火頭，包括梯間及天台，認為有可疑，交警方跟進。<br />\n<br />\n網上有片段拍攝到天台一名南亞居民無路可走驚險一刻。片段所見，當時該南亞漢身處最高層，火勢包圍下無路可走，只能危站大樓邊緣的晾衫架。然而火勢越來越大，即使消防試圖從樓下射水灌救亦無補於事。<br />\n<br />\n最後該南亞漢冒險一跳，由晾衫架飛躍過隔離華豐街6號的較低樓宇，兩座樓宇之間相距約3米，幸最後安全著陸於對面天台。有居於同一大廈數年的居民表示，未曾見過該南亞漢，但警方調查後，證實他為大廈住戶。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210303/RQM7ZK3535ARHCZ72AVZSAMSRE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2Jq6rFpSQv2afC6nNRcda8---yzPog8lwZohO5cV0PyNKIv34csGldGcA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210303%2FRQM7ZK3535ARHCZ72AVZSAMSRE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2Jq6rFpSQv2afC6nNRcda8---yzPog8lwZohO5cV0PyNKIv34csGldGcA&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiX4CLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=1ba1da83\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210303%2FRQM7ZK3535ARHCZ72AVZSAMSRE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2Jq6rFpSQv2afC6nNRcda8---yzPog8lwZohO5cV0PyNKIv34csGldGcA&h=ea3c188e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210303/RQM7ZK3535ARHCZ72AVZSAMSRE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2Jq6rFpSQv2afC6nNRcda8---yzPog8lwZohO5cV0PyNKIv34csGldGcA</a>"},{"pid":"3481c5db642c8f7e4f10c8ba10e47f2d712078cf","tid":2431634,"uid":550,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T20:16:48.000Z","msg":"以前嘉利大火有條友喺窗邊飛身撲埋去雲梯度爬落街，潛能真係要逼出嚟"},{"pid":"1c6dfe4f7a0fd566f06120a077d5332e870b5af8","tid":2431634,"uid":145056,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T20:18:08.000Z","msg":"連登仔：其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aae49317c1cfb41c15d5ce4b7504194477b4146","tid":2431634,"uid":67840,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T20:18:13.000Z","msg":"關禮傑"},{"pid":"abfdeb42bfd2844d57c804682d157a1aa9ff92d9","tid":2431634,"uid":50931,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3481c5db642c8f7e4f10c8ba10e47f2d712078cf","tid":2431634,"uid":550,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T20:16:48.000Z","msg":"以前嘉利大火有條友喺窗邊飛身撲埋去雲梯度爬落街，潛能真係要逼出嚟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T20:19:14.000Z","msg":"嘉利大火真係好撚恐怖，唔搏下跳出去監生燒死仲痛苦"},{"pid":"b59d721e0027a79ca97ad4d310ab48683b44db6f","tid":2431634,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T20:21:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1973c8396d182c06d2dc48c0f1dbd3baf3d2515c","tid":2431634,"uid":245819,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T02:25:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pYMBRwq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpYMBRwq.gif&h=312dc41b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f1b7df61801985cb5ae28b8e45dc48c6390772c","tid":2431634,"uid":17103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T02:29:57.000Z","msg":"關禮傑"},{"pid":"8afc977400ee8d1ccd23bc10e96fa691cc192d7f","tid":2431634,"uid":245819,"lik